    "source": "IFRS_9",
    "type": "main",
    "title": "Chapter 7 Effective date and transition",
    "subtitle": "7.3 Withdrawal of IFRIC 9, IFRS 9 (2009), IFRS 9 (2010) and IFRS 9 (2013)",
    "subsection": null,
